This beautiful all brick home with an in ground pool is located inside the city limits of Danielsville, but gives the feel of seclusion and tons of privacy! 3/2 with finished basement, beautiful sunroom overlooking the 18x36 pool with new liner installed in 2015.  This home is situated on 3.38 acres and  within a stones throw away from the high school.
